{"title":"Tomcat启动成功没有报错，但网页打不开","date":"2018-04-27T02:53:00.000Z","link":"post/55","tags":["his","tomcat","war","webapp","目录"],"categories":["Other"],"updated":"2019-04-27T13:31:32.052Z","content":"<p>错误情况：今天部署war包时，已经<code>unzip his.war -d ROOT/</code> ，并且<strong>tomcat start 成功</strong>，但网页却打不开。</p>\n<p>问题原因：当<strong>his.war包</strong> 放到<code>webapp/</code>目录下，解压完成后，没有删除<strong>war</strong>包。当<strong>tomcat</strong>再启动的时候会自己解压<strong>webapp</strong>目录下的<strong>war</strong>，这时<strong>tomcat</strong>不明白启动那个，所以导致这样的问题。</p>\n<p>解决方法：在<strong>tomcat</strong>启动前<strong>删除</strong>已经解压的<strong>war包</strong></p>\n","prev":{"title":"win7下用xampp部署php项目","link":"post/58"},"next":{"title":"Mybatis报错org.mybatis.spring.MyBatisSystemException","link":"post/54"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/55/"}